      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Fooled in the Flooded Forest",
        "Client": "Fainted(?) Hunter",
        "Description": "Shhh! Don\u0027t mind me! I ran into\r\na Chameleos and now I\u0027m stalling\r\nfor time playing possum. But I\r\ndon\u0027t think I can fool it for much\r\nlonger! If you can take care\r\nof it for me, I\u0027ll teach ya my\r\ntrick for getting out of a bind!",
        "Target": "Slay a Chameleos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Tromperie \u00E0 la For\u00EAt inond\u00E9e",
        "Client": "Chasseur \u00E9vanoui (?)",
        "Description": "Chut ! Fais comme si j\u0027\u00E9tais\r\npas l\u00E0 ! Je fais le mort pour\r\n\u00E9viter un Chameleos, mais combien\r\nde temps \u00E7a va marcher encore...\r\nOccupe-toi de lui, et je\r\nt\u0027apprendrai mon astuce pour\r\npasser inaper\u00E7u en cas de p\u00E9pin !",
        "Target": "Tuer un Chameleos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Inganno nella Foresta inondata",
        "Client": "Cacciatore svenuto(?)",
        "Description": "Shhh! Non badare a me. Mi sono\r\nimbattuto in un Chameleos e\r\nsto fingendo di essere morto!\r\nNon credo di poterlo ingannare\r\nancora a lungo. Se mi aiuti,\r\nti insegner\u00F2 il mio trucco per\r\ncavarsi da ogni impiccio!",
        "Target": "Uccidi un Chameleos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Faule Tricks im Flutwald",
        "Client": "Bewusstloser(?) J\u00E4ger",
        "Description": "Pst! Ich bin einem Chameleos\r\nbegegnet und jetzt stelle ich\r\nmich tot. Aber ich f\u00FCrchte, er\r\nwird mich bald durchschauen!\r\nErledige ihn, dann bring ich\r\ndir meinen Trick bei, mit dem\r\ndu aus der Klemme kommst!",
        "Target": "Erlege einen Chameleos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Enga\u00F1o en el Bosque inundado",
        "Client": "Cazador desmayado(?)",
        "Description": "\u00A1Chist! \u00A1Ign\u00F3rame! He visto\r\ncerca un Chameleos y me hago\r\nel muerto para evitarlo.\r\nPero no creo que pueda mantener\r\nla farsa por mucho tiempo;\r\n\u00A1enc\u00E1rgate de \u00E9l y te ense\u00F1ar\u00E9\r\nmi truco para salir de apuros!",
        "Target": "Abate un Chameleos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041E\u0431\u043C\u0430\u043D \u0432 \u0417\u0430\u0442\u043E\u043F\u043B\u0435\u043D\u043D\u043E\u043C \u043B\u0435\u0441\u0443",
